
A simple raytracing tool for X-Rays.

This raytracing tool has been primarily developed for tracing of
X-Ray Imaging Crystal Spectrometers on the fusion experiments
ITER and W7-X. It it however a general purpose tool, and can be
extended for use for any x-ray or optical raytracing applications.

